GNU/Hex
=====
this system has flexible configuration of both packages, file systems, and the kernel itself.
it made for direct computer's components access.
the project is inspired by the GNU ideology and is promoted on C and NASM x86-16.

source at src/
documentation at docs/
other files at storage/

